sub_title: Store Replenishment Specialist at Ahold Czech Republic
summary:
Within Supply Chain dept. I was responsible for supporting Operations, Supply Chain and Commercial department with replenishment ordering systems. 

Further responsibilities: Analyzing and setting up parameters for ordering of goods to 297 stores in Czech Republic, updating procedures and user manuals, solving issues concerning the ordering tools and communicating all changes and new initiatives regarding ordering systems. 

The last year I was a leader of two projects, I was responsible for many department initiatives and participated on several company initiatives.

school.name: Prague University of Economics and Business

profile_positions.description:
Technical support of replenishment ordering systems, optimizing of Stock amount on stores via modifying goods flow from distribution centres to stores. 
- Daily solving operational issues
- Coordinating and supervising individual system initiatives 
- Data analyzing, interpretation of data and solution propsal 
- Implementing a new software system for store ordering 
--- Defining system setup 
--- Testing of the system 
--- Organizing the development and implementation 
--- Roll out to 290 stores
--- IT and business documentation 
--- Modelling of procedures and user manuals 
--- Organizing of trainings 
- Development and up-grading of the system 

Leading several initiatives and 2 projects in the field of Supply Chain efficiency improvement.
profile_positions.title: Store Replenishment Specialist

profile_positions.description:
Responsible for products imported to Ahold Central Europe (Czech Republic, Slovakia, Poland, Latvia and Lithuania) from Far East and from European countries. 
- Organizing of Buying Meetings (selection of items imported) for Commercial dept. 
- Negotiation with suppliers regarding price and packaging (design and technical criteria) 
- Manage timing and logistics conditions with suppliers 
- Manage certifications (technical and safety criteria) and instruction manuals 
- Order settings 
- Solving Ahold and customers complains towards suppliers 
- Analyzing and forecasting of import volumes for next periods
